high_descs: Turn to your right walk toward the door then turn left face the end of the counter
Pick up the bottle beside the tomato on the counter
Turn to your left and head to the fridge
Open the fridge the put the bottle inside and out then close the fridge
Turn to your right then walk straight turn to your left
Put the bottle on the sink counter in front of the toaster
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bottle on the sink counter

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, then turn left at the wall to face the counter.
Pick up the wine bottle on the counter, to the right of the tomato.
Turn left, go straight, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the wine bottle in the fridge.
Turn right, go straight, then turn left at the end of the counter.
Put the wine bottle on the counter, in front of and to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wine bottle on the counter.

high_descs: Move right until you hit the wall, then turn to face your left
Pick up the bottle from off of the kitchen counter
Turn around so that you are facing the fridge
Put the bottle inside the fridge for a few seconds to cool and then take it out
Walk right and then turn to your left to face the toaster
Set the bottle down on the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: Chill a bottle and set it down on the counter
